<% include partials/header %>

<div class='text-center'>
    <h4>Troubleshooting</h4>
</div>

<div class='container'>
    <p class='lead ml-2'>Adding a stamp</p>
    <div id="accordion">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
          <h5 class="mb-0">
            <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
              How do I upload an image?
            </button>
          </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordion">
          <div class="card-body">
            We do not host images on our site, and therefore you cannot upload an image. Rather, you will paste the URL of a publicly available image. You can right-click on the desired image, select 'copy image address', and then paste this URL into the 'image' field of the add a stamp page. Please make sure the image you submit does not have any use restrictions (such as copyright).
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card mb-2">
        <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
          <h5 class="mb-0">
            <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
              I submitted my stamp - why can't I see it?
            </button>
          </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordion">
          <div class="card-body">
            All stamps must be approved by the webmaster before they are added to the site and available to be added to your passport.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    
      <p class='lead ml-2'>My passport</p>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
          <h5 class="mb-0">
            <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
              What are the levels, and how do I advance?
            </button>
          </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordion">
          <div class="card-body">
            Levels are simply a reflection of how many neighborhoods you have completed. The levels are as follows:
            <ul>
                <li>Tourist (i.e., no neighborhoods completed)</li>
                <li>Hipster Apprentice</li>
                <li>Hipster</li>
                <li>Junior Diplomat</li>
                <li>Diplomat</li>
                <li>Ambassador</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header" id="headingFour">
          <h5 class="mb-0">
            <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
              Why don't I see any stamps on My Passport?
            </button>
          </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseFour" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-parent="#accordion">
          <div class="card-body">
            Make sure you have a neighborhood selected first, and then click 'See Neighborhood Stamps'. 
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>

<% include partials/footer %>
